        {
            "id": 6318917,
            "title": "〈台股盤後〉又見新高！電子股開趴狂嗨大漲499點 上市櫃成交量再破兆元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>台股今 (22) 日明顯回神，權王台積電領軍電子權值股強攻，指數一度衝上 31890 點，飆漲 644 點，再度刷新歷史新高，終場漲幅略微收斂，達 499.71 點，收在 31746.08 點，收復五日線大關，成交量達 7910 億元，若計入櫃買市場交易量 2127 億元，單日成交量再度突破兆元大關，凸顯市場交投相當熱絡。</p></section><p><template id=\"P:1\"></template></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>權值股今日普遍走強，台積電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2330:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2330\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2330-TW</a>)(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:TSM:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/TSM\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">TSM-US</a>) 上漲超過 1%，終場收在 1760 元，台達電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2308:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2308\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2308-TW</a>) 今日在多頭簇擁下，直奔漲停板 1245 元，再度改寫新天價，市值也連帶提升至 3.23 兆元，超越鴻海 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2317:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2317\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2317-TW</a>) 成為台股第二大市值股，單一個股貢獻漲點 87.84 點，鴻海與聯發科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2454:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2454\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2454-TW</a>) 今日也都有 1% 至 2% 左右的漲幅，推升整體大盤走勢。</p></section><section>\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>其他權值股，如日月光投控 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3711:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3711\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3711-TW</a>)(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:ASX:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/ASX\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">ASX-US</a>)、廣達 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2382:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2382\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2382-TW</a>)、緯穎 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6669:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6669\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6669-TW</a>)、鴻勁 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:7769:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/7769\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">7769-TW</a>)、國巨 *(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2327:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2327\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2327-TW</a>) 等漲幅至少都在 2% 以上，國巨 * 更在華新科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2492:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2492\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2492-TW</a>) 漲價利多帶動下，飆漲將近 7%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>盤面今日百花齊放，PCB、重電、電源、電池等相關概念股全面走強，包括尖點 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8021:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8021\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8021-TW</a>)、健鼎 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3044:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3044\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3044-TW</a>)、大亞 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1609:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1609\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1609-TW</a>)、士電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1503:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1503\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1503-TW</a>)、光寶科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2301:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2301\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2301-TW</a>)、順達 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3211:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3211\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3211-TW</a>) 等皆亮燈漲停。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
            "link": "https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6318917",
